snippet.title: Amber Heard 's parents sided with Johnny because they knew ! More of her BS
snippet.description: RIP Paige Heard .  I really dont want to talk about her but is needed to show the weird dynamic that she had with them and them towards Johnny . Also I dont think some people understand how bruises work or look like or how lights hit on her face on that elevator footage ! shadows ! that simple .
